Perfect location for the holiday season😍
📍Location: Jawai Bandh (Dam) , Rajasthan

👉🏻Jawai Bandh is a beautiful dam in Rajasthan’s Pali district, surrounded by hills and nature.
👉🏻It’s known for its rich wildlife, especially leopards, crocodiles, and many kinds of birds. You can often see crocodiles sunbathing or hunting, and leopards resting on the rocks.
👉🏻The weather is pleasant, and the peaceful surroundings make it a great place to relax and explore. 
👉🏻To see the wildlife up close, you can take a leopard safari in the area😍

Body shaming has become so normal that we often don’t even recognize it as cruelty anymore. We laugh it off, we pass comments without thinking, and we forget that behind every body is a soul carrying a story. Sometimes, it’s a child quietly absorbing every word, every stare, every joke until those words become their inner voice. We don’t always see the damage being done, but it’s there. 
So please… let’s be gentler with our words, softer with our judgments, and kinder with our hearts. You never know what someone is going through, especially a child who’s still learning how to love themselves.
.
.
.
